---
const title = "SimpleUnitTools";
const description =
  "Simple unit conversions, calculators, and practical explanations for everyday and technical use.";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <link rel="canonical" href={new URL(Astro.url.pathname, Astro.site).toString()} />
    <meta property="og:title" content={title} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={description} />
    <meta property="og:url" content={new URL(Astro.url.pathname, Astro.site).toString()} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --max: 900px;
        --text: #111;
        --muted: #333;
        --border: #d8d8d8;
        --link: #551a8b;
        --card-bg: #fff;
        --shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        --accent-bg: #f0f9ff;
        --accent-border: #c7e5ff;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--text);
        background: #fff;
      }

      main {
        max-width: var(--max);
        margin: 2rem auto;
        padding: 0 1rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
      }
      .hero {
        background: var(--accent-bg);
        border: 1px solid var(--accent-border);
        padding: 1.4rem;
        border-radius: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      .hero h2 {
        margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: var(--text);
      }
      .hero p {
        margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .updates {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
      .updates strong {
        color: var(--text);
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      header p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      hr {
        border: 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        margin: 1rem 0 1.4rem;
      }

      /* === Popular Tools (3 columns) === */
      .popular-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 1.4rem;
        margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
      }

      .card {
        border: 1px solid #e3e3e3;
        padding: 1.6rem 1.8rem;
        background: var(--card-bg);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .card h2 {
        white-space: nowrap;
        margin: 0 0 0.8rem;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .card ul {
        font-size: 1.02rem;
      }

      .card li {
        margin: 0.72rem 0;
      }

      ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
      }

      a {
        color: var(--link);
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      section h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin: 1.2rem 0 0.6rem;
      }

      footer {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      /* === Tech & Networking block === */
      .big-box {
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: #fff;
        padding: 28px;
        margin: 18px 0 28px;
      }

      .two-col {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
        align-items: start;
      }

      /* Slight emphasis for center column */
      .popular-grid .card:nth-child(2) {
        border-color: #d0d0d0;
      }

      /* Responsive */
      @media (max-width: 780px) {
        h1 {
          font-size: 2.2rem;
        }

        .popular-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .two-col {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        section h2 {
          font-size: 1.8rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main>
      <header>
        <h1>SimpleUnitTools</h1>
        <p>
          Simple unit conversions, calculators, and practical explanations for
          everyday and technical use.
        </p>
        <hr />
      </header>

      <section class="hero">
        <h2>Tools that answer questions, not just numbers</h2>
        <p>
          Each calculator now explains why it exists, how people like you use it,
          and what real decisions it supports — shipping a new product, planning
          a launch, fixing a home project, or choosing the right data plan.
          Scroll down to see the latest updates and which tool suits your next
          task.
        </p>
        <div class="updates">
          <div>
            <strong>Latest refresh: </strong>
            <span>Feb 20 — new fuel consumption page with MPG / L per 100km comparisons, real-world cases, and FAQs.</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>Why it matters for you:</strong>
            <span>This site now deliberately pairs calculators with stories, case notes, and checklists that match your Amazon/Walmart workflow.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="hero" style="margin-top:-0.5rem;">
        <h2>New: AI赚钱专题</h2>
        <p>
          如果你在找“AI副业怎么开始、怎么选工具、怎么落地执行”，可以从
          <a href="/ai-money/">AI赚钱指南与工具库</a> 开始。
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Popular Tools -->
      <div class="popular-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Basic Converters</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/cm-to-inch/">cm to inch converter</a></li>
            <li><a href="/inch-to-mm/">inch to mm converter</a></li>
            <li><a href="/liter-to-gallon/">liter to gallon converter</a></li>
            <li><a href="/kg-to-lb/">kg to lb converter</a></li>
            <li><a href="/mph-to-kmh/">mph to km/h converter</a></li>
            <li><a href="/c-to-f/">°C to °F converter</a></li>
            <li><a href="/bytes-to-mb/">bytes to MB converter</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>Advanced Tools</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/fuel-consumption-converter/">Fuel consumption calculator</a></li>
            <li><a href="/download-time-calculator/">Download time calculator</a></li>
            <li><a href="/ohms-law-calculator/">Ohm’s Law calculator</a></li>
            <li><a href="/Mortgage-Calculator/">Mortgage Calculator</a></li>
            <li><a href="/binary-vs-decimal-storage/">Binary vs Decimal storage</a></li>
            <li><a href="/speed-unit-converter/">Speed unit converter</a></li>
            <li><a href="/Investing/">Compound Interest</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>Specialized Tools</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/cooking-measurement/">Cooking measurement</a></li>
            <li><a href="/inch-fraction-converter/">Inch fraction converter</a></li>
            <li><a href="/screen-size-calculator/">Screen size calculator</a></li>
            <li><a href="/pace-calculator/">Pace calculator</a></li>
            <li><a href="/stone-weight-converter/">Stone weight converter</a></li>
            <li><a href="/dpi-vs-ppi/">DPI vs PPI explained</a></li>
            <li><a href="/hz-vs-fps/">Hz vs FPS explained</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tech & Networking Explained -->
      <section>
        <h2 style="font-size: 3.2rem; margin: 0 0 12px;">
          Tech & Networking Explained
        </h2>

        <div class="big-box">
          <div class="two-col">
            <div>
              <h2>Popular Tools</h2>
              <ul>
                <li><a href="/mbps-vs-mbs/">Mbps vs MB/s explained</a></li>
                <li><a href="/download-time-calculator/">Download time calculator</a></li>
                <li><a href="/file-transfer-time-calculator/">File transfer time calculator</a></li>
                <li><a href="/bit-vs-byte/">Bit vs Byte explained</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h2>Related Converters</h2>
              <ul>
                <li><a href="/bytes-to-mb/">bytes to MB converter</a></li>
                <li><a href="/speed-unit-converter/">Speed unit converter</a></li>
                <li><a href="/mph-to-kmh/">mph to km/h converter</a></li>
                <li><a href="/liter-to-gallon/">liter to gallon converter</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Size & Specs Explained</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/amps-volts-watts/">Amps vs Volts vs Watts</a></li>
          <li><a href="/awg-wire-size/">AWG wire size explained</a></li>
          <li><a href="/noise-decibel/">What does dB mean?</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <hr />

      <footer>
        © 2026 SimpleUnitTools ·
        <a href="/about/">About</a> ·
        <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a> ·
        <a href="/disclaimer/">Disclaimer</a>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
